if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_shop')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_shop
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_shop */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_shop (
ShopID int identity,
PlatformID int not null,
ShopName nvarchar(200) not null,
Account nvarchar(200) not null,
Currency int not null,
Lrish decimal(3,1) not null,
Status int not null,
AddTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
telephone nvarchar(20) null,
zipcode nvarchar(20) null,
shopaddress nvarchar(200) null,
country nvarchar(20) null,
constraint PK_BASE_SHOP primary key (ShopID)
)
go
